-----BEGIN RSA PRIVATE KEY-----
PLACEHOLDER — REPLACE WITH YOUR AWS IoT DEVICE PRIVATE KEY.

This file is embedded into the firmware (EMBED_TXTFILES) as the mutual-TLS
client private key (plaintext, for the POC). Overwrite it with the private key
returned when you created the device certificate.

For production this is where the DS peripheral / esp_secure_cert swap goes:
flip NetworkContext.use_secure_element + ds_data in mqtt_client.c — no protocol
change. Do NOT commit a real private key to a shared repo.
